## Product Instructions

Read the full product skill for all rules, templates, and architecture:

```
/root/aisell/products/simple_dashboard/SKILL.md
```

Key rules (summary):
- Always save as `index.html` (never dashboard.html, report.html, etc.)
- Single-file SPA: Tailwind CSS + Chart.js via CDN only
- Use `tt()` for i18n (EN default, RU if browser language starts with ru)
- Auth: платформа управляет авторизацией автоматически (Magic Link, Invite через Google, Extension).
  НЕ реализуй auth вручную. Подробности — в SKILL.md секция "Система авторизации".
